1
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:55,000
"Lost To You"

2
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,700
(Episode 10)

3
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:02,299
If happiness has an expiration date,

4
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:04,499
then before it expires,

5
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:09,500
let's carve it into our bones.

6
00:01:12,833 --> 00:01:14,142
Brother, we're open for business!

7
00:01:14,166 --> 00:01:15,166
Thank you, everyone.

8
00:01:17,416 --> 00:01:19,000
Things will only get better from here.

9
00:01:19,208 --> 00:01:20,208
They will.

10
00:01:21,958 --> 00:01:22,958
Thank you.

11
00:01:23,958 --> 00:01:24,958
Delicious!

12
00:01:25,750 --> 00:01:26,830
What would you like to eat?

13
00:01:26,958 --> 00:01:27,916
Coming right up. Just a moment.

14
00:01:27,917 --> 00:01:28,934
We'll have the signature dish.

15
00:01:28,958 --> 00:01:30,082
Fish soup and fishball noodles, right?

16
00:01:30,083 --> 00:01:30,750
Yes, exactly.

17
00:01:30,750 --> 00:01:31,375
Two orders, right?

18
00:01:31,458 --> 00:01:31,958
Here it comes!

19
00:01:32,125 --> 00:01:33,708
Boss, can I get a Coke?

20
00:01:34,458 --> 00:01:35,041
Enjoy your meal.

21
00:01:35,250 --> 00:01:36,250
Sure, thanks.

22
00:01:38,083 --> 00:01:38,458
Here are your noodles.

23
00:01:38,583 --> 00:01:39,583
Thank you so much.

24
00:01:41,916 --> 00:01:43,291
Alright, coming right up.

25
00:01:46,333 --> 00:01:47,333
Mom, you've worked hard.

26
00:01:47,541 --> 00:01:48,541
It's nothing.

27
00:01:49,750 --> 00:01:50,750
Eat more.

28
00:01:51,583 --> 00:01:52,583
What's wrong?

29
00:01:53,458 --> 00:01:54,083
Nothing, I'm fine.

30
00:01:54,375 --> 00:01:55,375
Are you okay?

31
00:02:05,708 --> 00:02:06,708
What are you taking?

32
00:02:10,541 --> 00:02:11,541
Vitamins.

33
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,059
I've been a bit tired lately,
just getting some nutrients.

34
00:02:14,083 --> 00:02:15,083
Are you sure you're okay?

35
00:02:15,208 --> 00:02:16,208
I'm fine.

36
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,000
Xiao Yuan.

37
00:02:18,243 --> 00:02:19,659
Go grab those drinks.

38
00:02:20,291 --> 00:02:20,666
Okay.

39
00:02:20,833 --> 00:02:22,500
Just a moment, coming right up.

40
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:26,684
Thanks for your hard work, Mom.

41
00:02:26,708 --> 00:02:27,892
It's nothing. You should eat too.

42
00:02:27,916 --> 00:02:28,916
Come on, let's eat.

43
00:02:29,083 --> 00:02:30,083
Let's eat.

44
00:02:30,458 --> 00:02:31,476
Xiao Xia hasn't tried this before.

45
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:32,041
Have some more.

46
00:02:32,125 --> 00:02:32,958
What... what is this?

47
00:02:33,083 --> 00:02:34,166
This is goose barnacles.

48
00:02:34,333 --> 00:02:35,000
You've never had it, right?

49
00:02:35,208 --> 00:02:36,333
Come on, everyone try some.

50
00:02:36,458 --> 00:02:37,041
- Try some.
- Thank you, Auntie.

51
00:02:37,166 --> 00:02:38,166
Thank you.

52
00:02:50,583 --> 00:02:51,125
Is it good?

53
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:52,500
Tastes good, right?

54
00:02:52,708 --> 00:02:53,958
Come on, let's all

55
00:02:54,583 --> 00:02:56,208
celebrate the grand opening!

56
00:02:56,833 --> 00:02:57,458
Cheers!

57
00:02:57,666 --> 00:02:58,583
Congratulations!

58
00:02:58,666 --> 00:02:59,541
Thank you. Cheers!

59
00:02:59,666 --> 00:03:00,375
Thank you, everyone.

60
00:03:00,376 --> 00:03:01,767
Auntie, there's no need
to be so polite with us.

61
00:03:01,791 --> 00:03:02,458
I'll be coming over for
free meals all the time.

62
00:03:02,541 --> 00:03:03,601
Just don't get tired of me.

63
00:03:03,625 --> 00:03:04,875
You're all welcome anytime!

64
00:03:05,041 --> 00:03:06,761
Auntie, I wish your new shop smooth sailing

65
00:03:06,958 --> 00:03:07,958
and great prosperity!

66
00:03:08,125 --> 00:03:09,208
Thank you.

67
00:03:09,458 --> 00:03:09,958
Mom,

68
00:03:10,208 --> 00:03:11,375
Sister Xia set up a new

69
00:03:11,458 --> 00:03:12,625
Instagram account for me.

70
00:03:13,083 --> 00:03:15,250
She wants to turn me into
the 'Fish Noodle Beauty'.

71
00:03:15,458 --> 00:03:16,250
Once I go viral,

72
00:03:16,333 --> 00:03:17,642
our shop will become even more popular!

73
00:03:17,666 --> 00:03:18,375
Really?

74
00:03:18,458 --> 00:03:19,726
Just don't let it affect your studies.

75
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:20,750
I know.

76
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:23,666
Come on, let's

77
00:03:24,194 --> 00:03:25,194
raise our glasses again.

78
00:03:25,458 --> 00:03:26,833
To a booming business,

79
00:03:27,416 --> 00:03:28,559
and to us being together forever!

80
00:03:28,583 --> 00:03:31,125
Together forever!

81
00:03:34,208 --> 00:03:35,208
Let's take a group photo.

82
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:36,458
For the grand opening,

83
00:03:36,583 --> 00:03:37,623
we need a family portrait!

84
00:03:37,791 --> 00:03:39,250
Great, let's take a photo together.

85
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:40,041
Then...

86
00:03:40,042 --> 00:03:41,402
You are all my wonderful children.

87
00:03:41,791 --> 00:03:42,791
Should we hang it here?

88
00:03:44,375 --> 00:03:45,750
Can we put it over there instead?

89
00:03:45,916 --> 00:03:46,916
Sure, that works.

90
00:03:51,708 --> 00:03:52,708
Come closer.

91
00:03:53,375 --> 00:03:54,375
Hurry up and come over.

92
00:03:54,458 --> 00:03:54,958
Hold on.

93
00:03:55,125 --> 00:03:56,208
Let me adjust the framing.

94
00:03:57,875 --> 00:03:58,333
Xu Yuan,

95
00:03:58,875 --> 00:03:59,955
get a little closer to Mom.

96
00:04:00,458 --> 00:04:01,458
Come on.

97
00:04:02,125 --> 00:04:03,125
Hurry up and get in here.

98
00:04:03,541 --> 00:04:04,541
Get ready.

99
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:06,750
Everyone, smile!

100
00:04:15,166 --> 00:04:16,166
Zhan Wang!

101
00:04:16,208 --> 00:04:16,708
Brother Wang!

102
00:04:16,791 --> 00:04:17,625
Zhan Wang! Zhan Wang!

103
00:04:17,750 --> 00:04:18,976
Zhan Wang, are you okay? Zhan Wang!

104
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,000
Brother Wang! Zhan Wang!

105
00:04:34,666 --> 00:04:35,786
Are the family members here?

106
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,666
I'm his brother.

107
00:04:37,833 --> 00:04:39,142
The situation is not looking good.

108
00:04:39,166 --> 00:04:41,206
The patient has a tumor
in his right temporal lobe.

109
00:04:41,708 --> 00:04:42,708
A tumor?

110
00:04:43,291 --> 00:04:44,041
What kind of tumor?

111
00:04:44,208 --> 00:04:45,375
Doctor, he's only eighteen.

112
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:46,625
How could he have a tumor?

113
00:04:46,833 --> 00:04:48,583
Doctor, please check again.

114
00:04:48,791 --> 00:04:50,071
He's just been too tired lately.

115
00:04:52,958 --> 00:04:53,958
Xiao Yuan,

116
00:04:55,125 --> 00:04:56,125
don't get too worked up.

117
00:04:57,125 --> 00:04:58,125
Our priority right now

118
00:04:59,375 --> 00:05:00,375
is his illness.

119
00:05:03,166 --> 00:05:04,166
Doctor,

120
00:05:04,666 --> 00:05:05,666
after the diagnosis,

121
00:05:06,083 --> 00:05:07,226
what are the treatment options?

122
00:05:07,250 --> 00:05:08,690
We must operate as soon as possible.

123
00:05:08,875 --> 00:05:11,195
The tumor is in a sensitive
location, so surgery is risky.

124
00:05:11,333 --> 00:05:12,041
But if we delay,

125
00:05:12,166 --> 00:05:13,375
a more dangerous situation

126
00:05:13,458 --> 00:05:14,538
could happen at any moment,

127
00:05:14,625 --> 00:05:15,705
such as a brain herniation.

128
00:05:16,125 --> 00:05:17,517
You, as his family, need
to discuss this quickly

129
00:05:17,541 --> 00:05:19,741
to decide on a treatment
plan and schedule the surgery.

130
00:05:20,166 --> 00:05:21,166
Also,

131
00:05:21,666 --> 00:05:23,458
does the patient know
about his condition?

132
00:05:30,791 --> 00:05:31,951
He probably doesn't know yet.

133
00:05:33,083 --> 00:05:34,243
I need to contact our family.

134
00:05:36,250 --> 00:05:37,250
Is he

135
00:05:38,208 --> 00:05:39,208
awake yet?

136
00:05:39,333 --> 00:05:39,875
Not yet.

137
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:42,166
But his vital signs
have stabilized for now.

138
00:05:42,416 --> 00:05:43,736
He'll be moved to a ward shortly.

139
00:05:44,250 --> 00:05:45,250
You can go see him then.

140
00:05:46,208 --> 00:05:47,208
Alright. Thank you.

141
00:05:53,791 --> 00:05:54,791
Brother Xu,

142
00:05:56,166 --> 00:05:57,166
How could this happen?

143
00:05:57,625 --> 00:05:59,291
How could he possibly have a tumor?

144
00:06:01,875 --> 00:06:03,875
When he first fainted
and came to the clinic,

145
00:06:05,333 --> 00:06:07,125
I suspected something was wrong with him.

146
00:06:11,166 --> 00:06:13,206
But no matter what I asked,
he wouldn't say a word.

147
00:06:15,708 --> 00:06:16,708
It's all my fault.

148
00:06:18,451 --> 00:06:20,491
I should have given him a
proper checkup back then.

149
00:06:31,791 --> 00:06:32,791
I'm to blame.

150
00:06:35,291 --> 00:06:37,083
I spent so much time with him,

151
00:06:42,916 --> 00:06:44,208
yet I didn't notice anything.

152
00:06:44,791 --> 00:06:46,041
I didn't notice a thing.

153
00:06:47,458 --> 00:06:49,125
I'm just a jinx.

154
00:06:49,708 --> 00:06:50,767
Brother, don't be like this.

155
00:06:50,791 --> 00:06:52,071
No one could have foreseen this.

156
00:06:53,958 --> 00:06:54,958
Brother.

157
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:12,250
Brother Wang.

158
00:07:13,041 --> 00:07:14,041
Brother Wang.

159
00:07:15,875 --> 00:07:17,075
Brother Wang, can you hear me?

160
00:07:17,625 --> 00:07:18,625
Yuan.

161
00:07:23,291 --> 00:07:24,291
What's wrong?

162
00:07:25,375 --> 00:07:26,375
Why the long face?

163
00:07:30,625 --> 00:07:31,625
It's nothing.

164
00:07:32,583 --> 00:07:35,583
I just got a bit too excited when we
were taking photos at the noodle shop.

165
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:38,030
My blood sugar probably dropped.

166
00:07:39,333 --> 00:07:41,333
The doctor is making a
mountain out of a molehill.

167
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,000
I'm fine.

168
00:07:46,041 --> 00:07:48,321
Brother Xu has already
contacted a better doctor for you.

169
00:07:50,333 --> 00:07:51,416
You'll be fine in no time.

170
00:07:59,958 --> 00:08:00,958
It's my own body.

171
00:08:03,083 --> 00:08:04,083
I know it best.

172
00:08:05,041 --> 00:08:06,281
There's no need to trouble him.

173
00:08:09,166 --> 00:08:10,166
Zhan Wang.

174
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,750
Why?

175
00:08:12,458 --> 00:08:14,000
You had headaches time and time again,

176
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:16,250
took medicine over and over,

177
00:08:20,313 --> 00:08:21,896
and felt unwell repeatedly.

178
00:08:24,708 --> 00:08:26,125
Why didn't you tell me?

179
00:08:30,659 --> 00:08:32,118
Is it because, to you,

180
00:08:34,166 --> 00:08:35,686
telling me wouldn't make a difference?

181
00:08:35,791 --> 00:08:36,791
No.

182
00:08:37,875 --> 00:08:38,875
Xu Yuan, that's not it.

183
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:46,250
Or is it

184
00:08:51,284 --> 00:08:53,701
that you never even
envisioned a future with me?

185
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,500
No.

186
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:58,660
I did think about our future.

187
00:09:00,833 --> 00:09:01,833
But I was terrified

188
00:09:04,333 --> 00:09:05,533
that I wouldn't have a future.

189
00:09:08,125 --> 00:09:10,205
Actually, when I first
found out about this illness,

190
00:09:12,416 --> 00:09:13,416
I was terrified too.

191
00:09:17,375 --> 00:09:19,295
I was scared I'd die and
no one would even know.

192
00:09:21,916 --> 00:09:23,416
But I had no one to talk to.

193
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,120
I never expected to meet you

194
00:09:33,958 --> 00:09:35,333
when I came here.

195
00:09:40,416 --> 00:09:42,000
Every single day I spent with you,

196
00:09:43,875 --> 00:09:45,625
felt like borrowed time.

197
00:09:47,458 --> 00:09:48,658
We played basketball together,

198
00:09:50,041 --> 00:09:51,041
tutored each other,

199
00:09:52,833 --> 00:09:53,993
watched the sunrise together,

200
00:09:55,291 --> 00:09:57,083
and just finished setting up the new shop.

201
00:09:59,541 --> 00:10:01,333
I thought I could live like this forever.

202
00:10:07,916 --> 00:10:08,833
I just never expected

203
00:10:08,916 --> 00:10:10,156
that my life would be so short.

204
00:10:10,541 --> 00:10:11,333
Brother Wang,

205
00:10:11,541 --> 00:10:12,041
I'm sorry.

206
00:10:12,458 --> 00:10:13,538
That's not going to happen.

207
00:10:15,125 --> 00:10:15,708
It won't.

208
00:10:15,916 --> 00:10:16,916
I'm sorry.

209
00:10:18,458 --> 00:10:19,458
You'll be fine.

210
00:10:20,666 --> 00:10:22,186
You're definitely going to get better.

211
00:10:22,583 --> 00:10:23,750
Yuan, I'm sorry.

212
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:26,916
You're going to get better.

213
00:10:27,166 --> 00:10:28,166
You can't leave me all alone.

214
00:10:28,166 --> 00:10:28,625
I'm sorry.

215
00:10:28,625 --> 00:10:29,625
Xiao Wang,

216
00:10:29,916 --> 00:10:30,916
what's wrong with you?

217
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:33,100
If you're sick, you need to get treated.

218
00:10:33,958 --> 00:10:35,598
You shouldn't get so worked up right now.

219
00:10:36,250 --> 00:10:37,250
Dad...

220
00:10:39,166 --> 00:10:40,333
is already on his way.

221
00:10:42,416 --> 00:10:43,541
Why did you tell him?

222
00:10:45,083 --> 00:10:46,375
To watch me die?

223
00:10:48,166 --> 00:10:49,583
He doesn't care about me at all.

224
00:10:49,750 --> 00:10:50,750
Xiao Wang,

225
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,541
he does care about you.

226
00:10:55,083 --> 00:10:56,083
He cares?

227
00:10:56,958 --> 00:10:58,998
All he cares about is the
Zhan family's reputation.

228
00:10:59,291 --> 00:11:00,811
He's just afraid I'll end up like you.

229
00:11:01,375 --> 00:11:02,000
If you're mad at your dad,

230
00:11:02,083 --> 00:11:03,203
why are you snapping at him?

231
00:11:06,625 --> 00:11:07,625
Brother Wang,

232
00:11:11,125 --> 00:11:12,245
with something this serious,

233
00:11:13,875 --> 00:11:15,333
I think your dad should know.

234
00:11:19,916 --> 00:11:21,041
My dad is not like your mom.

235
00:11:22,375 --> 00:11:23,695
He only cares about making money.

236
00:11:24,083 --> 00:11:25,563
All he cares about is his reputation.

237
00:11:26,416 --> 00:11:27,416
Whether I live or die,

238
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,000
he doesn't give a damn.

239
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:31,500
But you care about him,

240
00:11:32,458 --> 00:11:33,458
don't you?

241
00:11:38,583 --> 00:11:39,583
I don't.

242
00:11:40,250 --> 00:11:41,416
If you didn't care about him,

243
00:11:42,291 --> 00:11:43,583
you wouldn't be this angry

244
00:11:43,916 --> 00:11:44,916
and this sad.

245
00:11:45,041 --> 00:11:46,184
It's because you care about him

246
00:11:46,208 --> 00:11:47,208
that you're angry.

247
00:11:48,041 --> 00:11:48,666
You're sad

248
00:11:48,958 --> 00:11:50,476
because you feel he should care about you,

249
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,500
but he hasn't.

250
00:11:53,958 --> 00:11:54,458
Actually,

251
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:55,500
I'm actually...

252
00:11:56,625 --> 00:11:57,625
scared that we...

253
00:11:59,666 --> 00:12:01,500
Your dad has the medical resources,

254
00:12:04,666 --> 00:12:05,666
and you need him.

255
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:09,500
Just let him come.

256
00:12:11,375 --> 00:12:12,375
For your sake,

257
00:12:13,291 --> 00:12:14,291
and for ours.

258
00:12:18,958 --> 00:12:19,958
Xiao Wang.

259
00:12:24,291 --> 00:12:25,291
Whatever.

260
00:12:54,833 --> 00:12:55,833
It's okay.

261
00:13:00,416 --> 00:13:01,416
You are...

262
00:13:01,458 --> 00:13:02,458
This is ridiculous!

263
00:13:06,416 --> 00:13:08,136
Keeping something this big from the family!

264
00:13:09,291 --> 00:13:10,125
The plane is ready.

265
00:13:10,250 --> 00:13:11,767
We're heading back to
Jingzhou this afternoon

266
00:13:11,791 --> 00:13:13,631
for a full checkup and
to prepare for surgery.

267
00:13:13,708 --> 00:13:14,708
I'm not going back.

268
00:13:15,666 --> 00:13:17,306
How long are you going to keep acting up?

269
00:13:19,833 --> 00:13:20,291
Dad,

270
00:13:20,583 --> 00:13:21,583
I'm not acting up.

271
00:13:22,166 --> 00:13:23,366
I know exactly what I'm doing.

272
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:26,500
Let me introduce you.

273
00:13:31,708 --> 00:13:32,708
Xu Yuan,

274
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:34,375
my boyfriend,

275
00:13:34,583 --> 00:13:35,125
Zhan Wang.

276
00:13:35,250 --> 00:13:37,184
Do you have any idea what
nonsense you're talking?

277
00:13:37,208 --> 00:13:39,208
I'm clearer than I've ever been.

278
00:13:39,375 --> 00:13:41,000
Why are you just like your brother?

279
00:13:41,375 --> 00:13:42,767
What does this have to do with my brother?

280
00:13:42,791 --> 00:13:44,083
The one I love is Xu Yuan.

281
00:13:44,541 --> 00:13:45,750
This is my own choice.

282
00:13:45,833 --> 00:13:46,833
I'm not wrong.

283
00:13:53,833 --> 00:13:55,791
Young man, please step outside.

284
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:58,083
We have family matters to discuss.

285
00:14:06,166 --> 00:14:06,791
No need to leave.

286
00:14:07,083 --> 00:14:08,083
Right in front of him,

287
00:14:08,541 --> 00:14:09,125
let's make this clear.

288
00:14:09,250 --> 00:14:10,458
Look at the state you're in.

289
00:14:10,625 --> 00:14:12,916
And you still have time for this nonsense?

290
00:14:14,083 --> 00:14:16,416
You are coming back to
Jingzhou with me right now.

291
00:14:16,583 --> 00:14:17,823
Fine, I'll go back to Jingzhou.

292
00:14:18,041 --> 00:14:19,041
But take him with us.

293
00:14:19,208 --> 00:14:20,208
No way.

294
00:14:21,875 --> 00:14:23,125
Then I'm not going back.

295
00:14:23,291 --> 00:14:24,291
I'll just die right here.

296
00:14:24,666 --> 00:14:26,101
You've never treated me as your son anyway,

297
00:14:26,125 --> 00:14:27,525
and I don't have a father like you.

298
00:14:27,625 --> 00:14:29,000
You ungrateful brat!

299
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:30,250
I...

300
00:14:41,541 --> 00:14:42,541
Uncle,

301
00:14:43,416 --> 00:14:44,856
Zhan Wang needs treatment right now,

302
00:14:45,250 --> 00:14:46,290
and he also needs respect.

303
00:14:47,416 --> 00:14:48,496
What you're doing right now

304
00:14:49,666 --> 00:14:50,750
isn't helping him at all.

305
00:14:51,375 --> 00:14:52,416
Going back to Jingzhou

306
00:14:54,416 --> 00:14:55,416
is non-negotiable.

307
00:14:56,041 --> 00:14:57,041
Dr. Wang,

308
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:04,780
give him a thorough examination.

309
00:15:05,083 --> 00:15:06,083
Yes, sir.

310
00:15:08,125 --> 00:15:09,125
Everyone else,

311
00:15:09,625 --> 00:15:10,625
please step out.

312
00:15:14,083 --> 00:15:15,083
Don't you leave.

313
00:15:15,541 --> 00:15:16,541
Get your checkup.

314
00:15:17,291 --> 00:15:18,611
I'll come see you when it's done.

315
00:15:18,791 --> 00:15:19,791
Be good.

316
00:15:32,666 --> 00:15:34,583
Get some rest, and
don't do anything foolish.

317
00:15:41,625 --> 00:15:42,625
Keep a close eye on him.

318
00:15:57,208 --> 00:15:58,208
I'm sorry.

319
00:15:58,250 --> 00:15:58,750
Except for Mr. Zhan,

320
00:15:58,833 --> 00:15:59,873
no one is allowed in here.

321
00:16:01,583 --> 00:16:03,063
Can't you just take this soup inside?

322
00:16:03,291 --> 00:16:04,291
I'm sorry, but no.

323
00:16:08,041 --> 00:16:09,041
Xiao Yuan.

324
00:16:11,875 --> 00:16:12,875
Brother Xu.

325
00:16:15,541 --> 00:16:16,541
Xiao Yuan,

326
00:16:17,500 --> 00:16:18,000
give it to me.

327
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:19,540
How were the test results?

328
00:16:24,833 --> 00:16:25,833
Not very promising.

329
00:16:27,208 --> 00:16:28,625
But it's not completely hopeless.

330
00:16:29,868 --> 00:16:31,951
The medical facilities in
Jingzhou are much better.

331
00:16:32,916 --> 00:16:33,916
So,

332
00:16:34,777 --> 00:16:36,977
we should convince him to
go to Jingzhou for treatment.

333
00:16:39,166 --> 00:16:40,166
I understand.

334
00:16:40,416 --> 00:16:41,875
You've been by his side for days.

335
00:16:42,458 --> 00:16:43,498
Go back and get some rest.

336
00:16:47,291 --> 00:16:47,916
But I'm worried...

337
00:16:47,916 --> 00:16:48,916
Don't worry.

338
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:50,250
I'm here.

339
00:16:51,416 --> 00:16:52,416
Bian-bian

340
00:16:53,208 --> 00:16:54,528
will also help me look after him.

341
00:16:56,208 --> 00:16:56,791
Don't worry.

342
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,200
Leave it to Brother Xu and me.

343
00:17:02,875 --> 00:17:03,875
Okay.

344
00:17:14,083 --> 00:17:15,163
No unauthorized entry here.

345
00:17:16,125 --> 00:17:17,125
I'm his older brother,

346
00:17:18,208 --> 00:17:19,875
and the son of your boss.

347
00:17:21,041 --> 00:17:22,041
No matter what,

348
00:17:22,583 --> 00:17:23,903
you still have to call me Master.

349
00:17:24,208 --> 00:17:24,750
Master Zhan,

350
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,583
we're just following Mr. Zhan's orders.

351
00:17:28,458 --> 00:17:29,458
You guys leave first.

352
00:17:29,958 --> 00:17:31,875
I need to have a word with my brother.

353
00:17:32,041 --> 00:17:33,041
Yes, of course.

354
00:17:33,083 --> 00:17:34,083
Let's go.

355
00:17:44,833 --> 00:17:45,873
Xu Yuan made this for you.

356
00:17:46,208 --> 00:17:47,208
Where is Xu Yuan?

357
00:17:52,166 --> 00:17:53,166
Brother,

358
00:17:53,625 --> 00:17:54,625
help me get out of here.

359
00:18:17,208 --> 00:18:18,208
Get on.

360
00:18:20,333 --> 00:18:21,642
How did you sneak out of the hospital?

361
00:18:21,666 --> 00:18:22,666
I'm all better.

362
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:24,226
Shouldn't I be discharged if I'm fine?

363
00:18:24,250 --> 00:18:25,290
It doesn't work that fast.

364
00:18:25,916 --> 00:18:26,916
The doctor allowed it.

365
00:18:27,083 --> 00:18:28,267
I've been cooped up for too long.

366
00:18:28,291 --> 00:18:30,291
I needed to get some
energy from my lucky star.

367
00:18:30,833 --> 00:18:31,291
Get on.

368
00:18:31,416 --> 00:18:32,000
Skip class,

369
00:18:32,416 --> 00:18:33,458
and elope. Do you dare?

370
00:18:35,166 --> 00:18:36,166
Let's go.

371
00:18:38,416 --> 00:18:39,416
Hold on tight.

372
00:18:53,625 --> 00:18:54,625
Xu Yuan,

373
00:18:56,333 --> 00:18:57,541
we're eloping!

374
00:19:01,250 --> 00:19:02,250
Zhan Wang,

375
00:19:03,083 --> 00:19:04,083
focus on getting treated.

376
00:19:04,375 --> 00:19:05,935
Once you're better, we can go anywhere.

377
00:19:20,541 --> 00:19:21,541
Look,

378
00:19:22,333 --> 00:19:23,333
the sun is setting.

379
00:19:25,958 --> 00:19:27,438
It will rise again tomorrow as usual.

380
00:19:33,833 --> 00:19:34,833
But what about me?

381
00:19:39,875 --> 00:19:41,715
I won't let you ask such
depressing questions.

382
00:19:45,875 --> 00:19:46,875
Yuan,

383
00:19:48,833 --> 00:19:49,833
if,

384
00:19:54,333 --> 00:19:55,333
I mean, what if

385
00:19:57,583 --> 00:19:58,583
we eloped

386
00:20:00,375 --> 00:20:02,083
to a place where nobody knows us,

387
00:20:03,708 --> 00:20:04,748
where there's no sickness,

388
00:20:07,416 --> 00:20:08,625
and no pressure?

389
00:20:15,416 --> 00:20:16,416
Would you be willing?

390
00:20:17,833 --> 00:20:18,953
Don't talk about 'what ifs'.

391
00:20:22,083 --> 00:20:23,763
Wherever you want to go, I'll go with you.

392
00:20:25,665 --> 00:20:26,825
But I need you to get better.

393
00:20:35,166 --> 00:20:36,250
When I was little,

394
00:20:38,708 --> 00:20:39,833
my grandmother told me

395
00:20:41,083 --> 00:20:42,458
that if she was no longer around,

396
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:46,000
she would turn into the ocean.

397
00:20:48,625 --> 00:20:50,708
She'd be able to hear
whatever I say to her.

398
00:20:54,958 --> 00:20:55,958
Grandma,

399
00:20:57,250 --> 00:20:58,458
I've come to see you.

400
00:21:00,166 --> 00:21:01,166
Grandma.

401
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:04,208
Can you hear me?

402
00:21:06,250 --> 00:21:07,750
I found someone who loves me,

403
00:21:09,166 --> 00:21:10,750
and whom I love very much.

404
00:21:13,166 --> 00:21:14,291
His name is Xu Yuan.

405
00:21:16,125 --> 00:21:17,291
He's a really good man.

406
00:21:18,250 --> 00:21:19,250
You don't have to worry.

407
00:21:27,833 --> 00:21:28,833
Granny,

408
00:21:29,125 --> 00:21:30,125
I'm Xu Yuan.

409
00:21:31,125 --> 00:21:32,958
I will take good care of Zhan Wang.

410
00:21:33,666 --> 00:21:34,666
Please rest assured.

411
00:21:39,125 --> 00:21:40,125
Zhan Wang.

412
00:21:42,875 --> 00:21:44,195
I know you miss Granny very much,

413
00:21:51,166 --> 00:21:52,791
but I won't let you go see her so soon.

414
00:21:55,625 --> 00:21:56,745
I absolutely won't allow it.

415
00:22:14,458 --> 00:22:15,458
Zhan Wang.

416
00:22:16,208 --> 00:22:17,208
Zhan Wang.

417
00:22:17,708 --> 00:22:18,708
Zhan Wang.

418
00:22:19,125 --> 00:22:20,125
Zhan Wang.

419
00:22:39,666 --> 00:22:42,386
He stopped taking his medication
before running out of the hospital.

420
00:22:43,708 --> 00:22:46,568
He even refused today's dehydration
therapy to lower intracranial pressure.

421
00:22:47,375 --> 00:22:48,375
He did it on purpose.

422
00:22:49,208 --> 00:22:50,208
He...

423
00:22:50,666 --> 00:22:52,186
He doesn't want to be treated anymore.

424
00:23:26,125 --> 00:23:27,125
Zhan Wang.

425
00:23:31,750 --> 00:23:32,916
Didn't you promise me

426
00:23:34,666 --> 00:23:36,906
that we'd open Yuan's Noodle
House all over the country?

427
00:23:38,666 --> 00:23:40,586
Didn't you promise to
watch the sunrise with me?

428
00:23:42,541 --> 00:23:43,541
Zhan Wang.

429
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,166
You're breaking your word.

430
00:23:48,791 --> 00:23:49,791
Xu Yuan.

431
00:23:51,958 --> 00:23:54,125
I know the success rate
of this surgery is very low.

432
00:23:55,666 --> 00:23:56,666
And...

433
00:23:57,166 --> 00:23:58,246
even if I have the surgery,

434
00:24:00,208 --> 00:24:01,458
I might go deaf,

435
00:24:02,666 --> 00:24:03,666
go blind,

436
00:24:05,625 --> 00:24:06,825
and I'd have to shave my head.

437
00:24:09,541 --> 00:24:10,541
Why don't you

438
00:24:11,166 --> 00:24:13,583
just remember how
handsome I look right now?

439
00:24:14,875 --> 00:24:15,875
Wouldn't that be better?

440
00:24:21,291 --> 00:24:22,291
No, it wouldn't.

441
00:24:25,708 --> 00:24:27,125
No matter what you become,

442
00:24:31,041 --> 00:24:32,625
I want to be with you.

443
00:24:34,708 --> 00:24:35,708
Zhan Wang,

444
00:24:36,583 --> 00:24:37,875
just do it for me.

445
00:24:39,125 --> 00:24:40,125
Try one more time.

446
00:24:43,375 --> 00:24:44,916
Try one more time, please?

447
00:24:45,666 --> 00:24:46,916
Try one more time.

448
00:24:50,041 --> 00:24:51,041
I'm begging you.

449
00:24:55,625 --> 00:24:56,708
I'm begging you.

450
00:25:03,708 --> 00:25:05,000
I'm begging you.

451
00:25:07,333 --> 00:25:08,333
Okay.

452
00:25:10,458 --> 00:25:11,458
For you.

453
00:25:52,750 --> 00:25:54,208
Amitabha.

454
00:25:55,916 --> 00:25:56,958
Young benefactor,

455
00:25:58,750 --> 00:26:01,291
an obsession in the heart
can be a curse or a blessing.

456
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:03,000
It can change in an instant.

457
00:26:03,416 --> 00:26:04,416
Master,

458
00:26:04,541 --> 00:26:05,041
I...

459
00:26:05,166 --> 00:26:07,250
I see that you,

460
00:26:07,458 --> 00:26:09,250
though bearing the sign of a lone star,

461
00:26:09,416 --> 00:26:11,176
actually harbor the
essence of a lucky star.

462
00:26:11,708 --> 00:26:13,268
Fortune and misfortune are intertwined,

463
00:26:13,625 --> 00:26:15,250
and the tide can be turned.

464
00:26:15,583 --> 00:26:16,708
Master, do you mean...

465
00:26:24,250 --> 00:26:24,958
Thank you, Master.

466
00:26:25,083 --> 00:26:26,875
Amitabha.

467
00:26:28,583 --> 00:26:30,791
All things in this world

468
00:26:31,583 --> 00:26:33,791
are impermanent and fleeting.

469
00:26:34,458 --> 00:26:36,625
From love comes longing,

470
00:26:37,208 --> 00:26:39,583
and from love comes sorrow.

471
00:26:40,250 --> 00:26:42,041
But if you find a kindred soul,

472
00:26:42,708 --> 00:26:45,958
all hardships shall cease.

473
00:26:56,791 --> 00:26:58,791
On December 12th,

474
00:26:59,291 --> 00:27:01,083
at exactly 4:15 PM,

475
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:03,250
at the place where the comet falls,

476
00:27:03,666 --> 00:27:05,125
make a sincere wish,

477
00:27:05,708 --> 00:27:07,750
to reverse the course of fate.

478
00:27:36,375 --> 00:27:37,375
Uncle,

479
00:27:37,916 --> 00:27:39,333
come on up. Let's talk.

